{"settings":"{

  "vsintellicode.modify.editor.suggestSelection": "automaticallyOverrodeDefaultValue",

  "git.suggestSmartCommit": false,

  "editor.wordBasedSuggestions": false,

  "[dart]": {

    "statusBar.debuggingBackground": "#8FBCBB",

    "statusBar.debuggingForeground": "#434C5E"
  },
  "settingsSync.ignoredSettings": ["-dart.flutterSdkPaths"],
  "todohighlight.exclude": [
    "**/node_modules/**",
    "**/bower_components/**",
    "**/dist/**",
    "**/build/**",
    "**/.vscode/**",
    "**/.github/**",
    "**/_output/**",
    "**/*.min.*",
    "**/*.map",
    "**/.next/**"
  ],
  "todohighlight.include": [
    "**/*.js",

    "**/*.ts",
    "**/*.tsx",
    "**/*.html",
    "**/*.php",
    "**/*.css",
    "**/*.scss"

  "todohighlight.keywords": [
    "DEBUG:",
    "REVIEW:",

      "text": "HACK:",
      "color": "#000",
      "isWholeLine": false
    }
  ],
  "todohighlight.isEnable": false,
  "git.confirmSync": false,
  "git.autofetch": true,
  "editor.renderWhitespace": "all",
  "editor.fontLigatures": true,

  "vim.leader": " ",

  "dart.normalizeFileCasing": true,

    "plaintext": false,

  "dartImport.fixOnSave": true,
  "vim.statusBarColorControl": true,

  "vim.vimrc.path": "$HOME/.vim/vimrc",

  "editor.cursorSurroundingLines": 8
